  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们要做一个用户旅程图，主题是「在网店寻找特定商品」。整体分成两大阶段：先进入网店，再寻找具体商品。第一阶段我想放「访问网站」和「登录（可选）」这两个步骤，你觉得登录这个可选步骤需要特别强调吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Enter online shop",
        "Visit website",
        "Log in (optional)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，登录标为可选是个好做法。那评分方面，访问网站给4分，登录因为是可选的给3分，这样区分度够吗？还是登录也要4分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit website",
        "Log in (optional)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "3分可以，体现它是可选步骤。第二阶段内容比较多，用户会浏览分类、进入有希望的分类、应用筛选条件、滚动浏览商品列表，最后点到具体商品。这些步骤评分都定4分，你看流程顺吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Look for specific product",
        "Check out categories",
        "Go to promising category",
        "Apply filter to category",
        "Scroll through products",
        "Go to promising product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第二阶段的前半部分已经加上了。那进入具体商品页面之后呢？还需要哪些步骤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go to promising product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "进入商品页面后，用户会阅读商品描述、查看商品变体、阅读评价，最后决定是否找到心仪商品。对了，「进入有希望的商品」这一步我觉得体验最关键，给5分，其他保持4分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Read product description",
        "Check out product variants",
        "Read reviews",
        "Decide if product found",
        "Go to promising product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，「进入有希望的商品」5分，其余描述、变体、评价、决策都是4分。整个旅程图标题是「Looking for a specific product」，两个section分别是「Enter online shop」和「Look for specific product」，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Looking for a specific product",
        "Enter online shop",
        "Look for specific product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，section标题我想调整一下，第二个用「Browse and select product」会不会更清楚？不对，还是保持「Look for specific product」吧，和主题更一致。另外确认所有步骤的执行者都是User。",
      "elements_involved": [
